description: The problem is a RuntimeError caused by an incorrect implementation of Memoization. The program is trying to store the results of a function call in a cache, but the cache is not being updated correctly when the function is called again with the same arguments. This results in the program returning the
output:
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "<stdin>", line 1, in <module>
IndentationError: expected an indented block
